 screen, where the current power mode is displayed. The options include:<\/p><ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>P (Paddle Assist) mode: Ideal for navigating the waters to reach the lineup<\/li>\n\n<li>L (Low), M (Medium), and H (High): Each mode offers varying degrees of assistance tailored to your weight, gear, and personal preferences&nbsp;<\/li><\/ul><p>Select your desired mode with a simple button press, and adapt your ride accordingly.<\/p><div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6154 lazyload\"\/><noscript><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"2240\" height=\"1260\" src=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6154 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1.jpg 2240w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1-60x34.jpg 60w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/1-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2240px) 100vw, 2240px\" \/><\/noscript><\/a><\/figure><\/div><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Secure mounting to ensure stability<\/h2><p>With power settings sorted, you\u2019ll want to ensure your controller stays securely in place throughout your ride. Your controller package includes two distinct mounting straps, each serving a specific purpose. Begin by prioritising safety\u2014attach the provided lanyard to your controller, mitigating the risk of loss in the event of an unexpected fall. Thread the lanyard around your paddle, ensuring it&#8217;s snug and secure.<\/p><p>Moving on to the mounting straps, choose between the two options provided, both designed for effortless attachment to your paddle or winging handle. With a firm grip on your controller, affix the strap to your preferred location, ensuring a tight fit. Repeat the process on the opposite side for added stability.<\/p><div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP\/\/\/yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6155 lazyload\"\/><noscript><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2240\" height=\"1260\" src=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-6155 lazyload\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2.jpg 2240w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2-60x34.jpg 60w, https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/06\/2-600x338.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2240px) 100vw, 2240px\" \/><\/noscript><\/a><\/figure><\/div><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">It&#8217;s time to ride<\/h3><p>Armed with the above, the waves await! You&#8217;re equipped to explore new horizons with your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/product\/complete-kit-black\/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/product\/complete-kit-black\/\">Stoke Foil Boost<\/a>. Be sure to check out the other options available to enhance your ride, like <a href=\"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/product\/xr-battery\/?v=6cc98ba2045f\">our new XR battery<\/a>, which will extend your foiling session. Happy riding.<\/p>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We\u2019re very proud of our controller. Whether you&#8217;re prone foiling, SUP foiling, or winging, having mastery over your equipment can make all the difference, so we made our controller easy to master. Powering on, navigating power settings, and securely mounting your controller are all easy to do and lead to an optimal experience on the [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":6156,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"rank_math_lock_modified_date":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[33],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-6152","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-stoke-foil-boost"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6152","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6152"}],"version-history":[{"count":3,"href":"https:\/\/www.stokefoiling.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6152\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":74